17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 6-127A, is
19 amended to read as follows:
20 Section 6-127A. A. The Oklahoma Legislature recognizes that
21 public school paraprofessionals play an important role in educating
22 school children and in assisting teachers. The Legislature further
23 recognizes the increasing role of public school paraprofessionals in
24 the school system in light of teacher shortages. To achieve the
